nummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7e82de4f-9a69-4e27-a67c-68522040907a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223806623533/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-1cbb56b0-96e9-45e8-8bb9-1c7db5916e81\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223806623533/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223806623533/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223806623533/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-4101916d-9615-4780-8684-4e967e96a31e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-156e84ba-4ae8-4562-ac8a-0b0c2d8c4089\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-81bb8efa-d230-4ee9-ad8d-dc33e90d7d5d\" style=\"\">회사소개서는 세로형이 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4a517379-6f78-4d94-bbed-54412ba82167\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-359d4892-16be-4c35-a2f0-7bab0af91df5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0b6e608f-8d03-40d1-987d-1afd988a31fd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">여러분이 새로운 사업을 시작한다면 지금 당장 고민해야 하는 것이 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b9c76090-5981-445c-a5cf-6629b8e244a2\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>회사소개서</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fcce562d-7e47-4b67-9881-94320faa1520\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 또는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-879b1677-44d8-4647-8d31-6490927450fb\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>사업계획서</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f795b402-2898-44f1-919c-fb6584bfe6c8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">일 겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-65ac0cfc-b65d-4e93-9fcd-8fba9ce7821d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-51bfcbc2-e910-4816-84c0-0803f0aa93fe\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-002a96ac-4a54-47b6-bb8c-519567ad76ea\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-daf6ed6b-5ab4-49e7-b6fd-95f964532500\" style=\"color:#555555;\">명칭이 어떻든 간에 회사를 홍보하기 위한 하나의 자료는 계속적으로 업데이트하여 관리하는 것이 좋습니다. 이것은 사이트 개발과 유사합니다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ef43d992-a7e6-48c9-ad79-fe5ed8f286c7\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">초반에 돈을 들여 홍보 카탈로그를 제작해 놓고 매년 성과를 담는 내용이나 추가된 서비스 등을 업그레이드하지 않는다면 그것은 흡사 사이트를 개발하고 관리를 하지 않는 것도 같습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1a9dbf62-345f-4ab3-8b14-05a8e12ef06d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-296813ed-55ad-4933-9d29-20882425cc64\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9ac4be67-4e6f-471f-b250-232abcd2f1ef\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d6ccee97-6bbf-418a-87b0-406bc8ea680e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄도 예전 같지 않게 소량 다품종 생산이 가능해진 만큼 몇천 부씩 홍보물을 만들어 놓고 사용하다가 내용이 바뀌어 다시 제작하는 오류(?)를 범하지 마십시오.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e9af595f-3433-43d7-9c26-66d28f31972c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b085dc7c-7b12-44fe-b631-daca44eb6d0f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-42065e69-9297-4184-9177-f4fadbb625d4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-23fa78fb-e282-4b4a-9a71-2e9c49133ba6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이제는 소량 100부 정도를 필요하실 때 제작하고 사용하시는 지혜가 필요할 때입니다. 그 이유는 고객님의 사업내용도 급변하는 시대의 트렌드에 맞게 계속적인 업데이트나 관리가 필수가 된 요즘이 된 까닭입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-857ab632-0f71-4330-98c2-6d9102388178\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-07cab9d1-2d5d-453b-b4f3-0df45f4bdb65\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5c916344-1119-4356-8c75-3009e498ae77\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e43da936-f44a-40e5-8826-41a564d8e046\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그럼 말하고자 하는 내용에 따른 분류를 한번 해보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6a28bf18-fd80-4203-891a-c8e9eb4a1e02\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-44a8211d-d4ff-4b08-8568-01303f7957ec\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e7532a5f-09a4-434c-ada9-db48235d2fcf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0eae2a7d-3844-4922-8bd0-201f15012467\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>회사소개서</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cf66ab18-bdd5-48f8-9c0c-13c95bd24c29\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b406b46e-5135-4f7b-8edd-0a88684d629e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">회사소개서는 대표적으로 회사의 사업내용이나 정보를 소개하는 홍보물입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f996aab9-415c-444f-9d89-085fb80109b6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c9f40d70-049a-458f-8309-dfbf560459d6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c6afaaef-0445-463e-b861-d880ba38f6f4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a6ffaba4-92e6-494e-9fa3-4dfbc8670eb8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이는 마치 회사 전체 홈페이지의 구성 내용과 유사하거나 일치합니다. 이런 이유로 대부분 전산개발 회사들이 홍보물 제작이나 인쇄물 디자인 영업도 병행하고 있는 까닭입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4f979b4e-57e7-40d2-9d9c-8f66106638da\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-08086366-c39b-46b0-9a66-975b35a8a735\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4102e157-f8ba-47b3-8f7e-818c131ec81b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8cac5280-edac-4be0-8fc6-27989817de95\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그 내용에는 다음과 같이 요약할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dc698700-0154-4ea9-99e0-5c63929799f1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f21efab3-789d-4c9b-a7dc-cbc4f7d80138\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-59ee1c4d-3a42-406b-8509-58351aa339c3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6718ec62-1694-48ef-be1a-c02d5fe0574a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>INTRO</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d70a5a88-d938-4bd1-9c92-6c8a63a76b8c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e2dea813-265c-4799-8c63-c16816a426a3\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>회사정보</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bbeb29bf-4848-4dee-a18d-4dc7aad8bf96\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> (인사말, 조직도, 고객센터 등)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a09d8c41-933a-4af1-928d-96d0d5ff1cab\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-34d6c0b3-0f75-4c45-977c-e45e53d9c06c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>브랜드 소개</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-70cd5c69-2cfb-4d44-b678-e19420b95a98\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> (CI/BI, 기타 이미지메이킹 자료)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-30ec7689-d232-4005-82c1-0f7d51ab4487\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2f3721f4-6bc6-402e-a831-83516c07ad7f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>제품 및 서비스 내용</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-00108e1e-1860-4523-a1ed-006f7e5568c7\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> (판매 상품이나 구축하는 서비스 내용)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0196ec4e-7ff7-4747-a8d2-6cf31f028ff0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-25c65b0f-0413-4222-8e40-569d705d1bee\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>기타</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5327cedb-c1fd-4c37-8c0b-76bce2983ff5\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> (지사, 요약 글 외 이야기하고 싶은 특정 내용 등)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d3318075-c8fc-460d-810e-c5d69463279a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223806623533/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-977862e8-80d6-4e60-951f-1ad868777c00\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-79e78549-6a8e-442a-9bb3-f568f389fcb2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-df84ee89-dbc1-42d4-b12c-52f51ec341d7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7972777e-8ab4-45f7-a09c-5d796ac2d8dd\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>서비스 소개서</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-008a24cf-0016-4603-996f-231a15f98051\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-99f32587-cfe4-4940-8f26-d86f5849176e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">서비스 소개서는 회사소개서와는 달리 그 회사가 구축하고 있는 서비스 중에 특징적인 부분만을 요약하여 집중적으로 이야기하는 홍보물입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-753c6fdc-fd9c-458d-a7c6-a308cdf3a543\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2cd87487-8123-43da-ac54-b3231a14dd1b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-931e2fd7-9eee-42a5-8b58-b289a4ab2a4b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-20fbd4dd-24fc-404b-801e-ec2fc87385f3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 홍보물에는 이 서비스의 구성이나 프로세스 또는 강점 위주나 서비스를 보다 디테일하게 설명하는 기획이 우선입니다. 회사의 홍보는 그다음 순위가 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e4e4d4b8-f40f-4108-bfd5-3cc638f748e8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8b83d057-ccce-4d34-852a-d0b305ccf1de\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-671baf92-5eeb-404c-a778-5d46ec368050\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d797f3e3-f190-4c08-8e07-b66cb4f65f67\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>INTRO</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a16d1a06-9a96-43c7-956f-1e5c537912ae\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-494cc028-f560-4674-a46f-a694351f2f30\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>간단한 회사정보</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4f196b0e-abda-40ff-9ce8-13f4446d3037\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> (기본 회사 정보 등)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6f5bd3d7-c505-4928-9742-5541c5ac22a6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ee77b8c4-fb22-43a1-897c-e7da6bb1a310\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>서비스 소개</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5b94bd53-d60c-481c-9731-b3b72a178c39\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> (서비스 런칭 이유, SWOT 분석, 서비스 프로세스 등)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5e986030-051e-4184-9d4f-0612f4c18892\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-61789390-d949-4a1a-b5f8-22d1c6a83a0e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>구체적인 서비스</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bcab97d4-8a2d-402b-af11-7e03a2e8815a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> (진행과정, 업데이트 계획, 파급효과 등)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b2f443ff-d122-4a16-b887-8fb18537544b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-81a571e1-af5c-42d3-8b16-f1211d637d71\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>기타</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-61d7e936-4a5e-482b-9e43-0414e962a1c9\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> (추가하고 싶은 서비스나 기타 등)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6152f30e-39ba-4104-abb9-4e07ea773328\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223806623533/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-218d80f8-5a7b-4adf-bc69-eded25fa515b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-eaeef1c7-a81d-4388-ad22-26471aac61b3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5f646338-64ca-413e-809c-56674780bafa\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-615d12c1-841c-4f31-b010-c9af86055ef8\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>서비스 프레젠테이션</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-18b30e85-f12f-4080-b03f-bf7f5bbaabfa\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4e2af691-407b-40bf-987c-0f2dde7549e2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">서비스 프레젠테이션은 소개서와는 달리 발표용에 의존하여 자료를 구성합니다. 이는 대부분 PPT나 PDF 파일로 만들고 배포는 PDF로 발표는 PPT로 하는 경우가 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-37c68328-e79d-4556-a231-bd8b4e60e1fd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-957bd5ba-6cf1-462e-8703-5e955198f268\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2b761dc6-4cff-4aa6-8944-fb8bdbbc359a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fb1bb6e9-ea03-4f76-9216-46b66b728fda\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그 유명한 스티브 잡스의 프레젠테이션 키노트는 지금도 발표용 자료로는 다시 봐도 우수한 내용과 기획이 담겨있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0485d447-1db9-4184-903f-fac306cf75fb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b6e2c3bf-6796-4d1e-bcfd-e6c38d3c4dc7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-91dd23a5-c4c2-4711-98d4-bd9921bba2cd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ba534c41-e754-44ea-a003-fc604f4e2bad\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 프레젠테이션의 핵심은 심플함과 단순함에 있다고 할 것입니다. PPT에 담겨있는 글자 하나를 설명하기 위해 수십 시간을 연습하고 집약해서 설명 노트에 담습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f9699174-b92d-4068-98c8-43fa67f9cd78\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cc203164-dd2a-4eed-a9e9-38fccc7736a2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0c4ba174-0347-4f98-ab42-63af10791fc2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-90b2131f-683f-46ee-99d5-1c002dc6a737\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>INTRO</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a264f9e4-259e-4b72-9599-55dfc2c80a37\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ace661ed-4d00-423c-9033-6b6a94730f33\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>서비스 키워드</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b990d81f-0b1c-4aba-a321-319602aa3289\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> (키 비주얼에 따른 핵심 내용 등)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-95735509-4c45-4dc1-bf6f-7ef527911536\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-846cfa20-a487-46d2-a7d6-b3c830c1a4e0\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>구체적인 서비스 진행</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-434e4b3e-c6fe-4ea5-b535-8ffb63e4048e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> (모션이나 이벤트에 따른 기획형 디자인)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0efcbd32-1708-4c2d-b3ed-9b22911bf72a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fb36ab1d-f528-4f8f-8b4a-8eb55c4380ff\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>기타</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c8086e55-0fa6-4933-b6c4-ecae68bcf104\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223806623533/006.PNG\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5a28149d-e379-4aeb-997b-6f8801c652b8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-169ed117-8734-4367-9561-7bc5ea52c7f8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f9511c64-7ecc-4885-9ed1-079573f620a9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7428b6e8-f4bc-4115-8b89-a58505e5f1b7\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>IR</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ca931115-35cc-427d-97c6-9205d4c7fbfd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-710cb90b-cf0b-4469-8a6a-73e38a57d9ba\" style=\"color:#555555;\">IR 보고서는 주로 1년간 회사의 모든 상황을 보고하는 형식의 문서입니다. 보통의 경우 PPT로 제작되지만 특별하게 디자인이 가미된 일러스트나 드로잉 톨로 제작된 PDF 파일 형태도 심심치 않고 볼 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cc82f0a0-ae11-475f-a185-4c90634f13ab\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cbec0208-eb6e-404c-8111-d031678084e6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-803d8ec6-fcee-44e9-9917-fa990c78d6a9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-326cbdfe-1c25-4f59-b885-041872a51714\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이는 조금 더 시각적으로 멋지고 편하게 볼 수 있도록 하는 회사의 배려이자 한 해 동안 이루어 낸 성과를 알려서 더 높은 단계의 투자를 이끌어 내는 도구로 활용되기도 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1cf9c13e-275a-4dc0-a777-a382cdf2704c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aa32a0d6-6873-4a39-9c03-fd4f310a1724\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f1ad3e55-3e3f-4195-97f0-66a8eb671fbd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4c547e3a-918a-4824-a788-8e2f5d0efaa2\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>INTRO</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b3d33a19-0b69-4712-bc83-22caa8b306e4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-830f954c-14a0-4f4e-8b8c-0e4964c7d774\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>회사정보</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bace6616-5b90-4b52-a001-71290bba4a5f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> (인사말, 조직도, 고객센터 등)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-77f2f29f-da05-4b55-8b3a-695294e48627\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a639f620-b84d-4227-8e39-13395f3bf667\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>브랜드 소개</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-12cd201e-8c74-4870-8ce6-a60481fcb735\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> (CI/BI, 기타 이미지메이킹 자료)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f7df24a1-6afb-4d2a-8f5c-72d6448b62c3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e45b5417-0c01-4461-bf7e-beccb2a9509f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>제품 및 서비스 내용</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f86a555d-d41e-4020-86aa-1f59f283707e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> (판매 상품이나 구축하는 서비스 내용)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b38b936a-c6c5-4ec7-b6c1-49e944ac77ae\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6192b336-b0ef-43e3-b03d-53a321320d09\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>재무제표</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a05a753c-f10d-4ceb-b69f-5aab1d19ddf1\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> (IR 보고서의 핵심)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f757d437-3460-44fd-91bf-b19773ac65a0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d2a9e1f9-5487-47cb-88b1-99f2741d828e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>향후 진행 및 투자계획</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-92ef7195-3782-49f9-b0d4-de36160a4fdd\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> (IR 보고서의 핵심)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ac749b69-bf56-49c3-a5be-0b8ee21f4b56\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-efbd7b46-57c6-4b5a-81a4-db3cdacd4437\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>기타</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-92191c7d-98b1-4bbb-b6c2-fb00114f459d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223806623533/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-31004cd0-a5f9-46a7-a9c2-1cbbd932cb02\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8424386d-5d29-43f4-ab1a-f7dd7c5e2385\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f25f9faf-37da-4194-bdef-a320c80557e6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-bbfdfbd4-3115-4adc-a48a-fa41e3d6a5dc\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>제품 카탈로그</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fc596bc5-efdd-474f-83df-afa1b2849508\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d0e306fc-2215-43ad-a18b-501593d65909\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제품 카탈로그는 고객님의 회사가 눈에 보이는 유형의 물건을 팔 때 그 상품을 홍보하기 위한 디자인 물이라고 보시면 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3536164d-2349-4077-ae51-62990e1dee02\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9f2d737e-c20a-4d42-8eba-883f2fb459a2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d2e42a9d-9d58-4c90-b0b7-2b0fc900bb80\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3efd6e66-6f01-4ea8-bc18-c4d9d95ffdb0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 인쇄물에서 가장 중요한 것은 제품 사진입니다. 제품 사진의 퀄리티가 이 홍보물 퀄리티의 절반 이상을 차지하게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eaf1c8ce-0886-4b74-acaa-397edd75ef05\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-43f3e06d-086b-49f7-925b-36a332da8226\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-365f8bf4-38dd-45de-b728-6827870854bb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6d2225a4-5461-4ece-a512-bc1ef1d0189c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>INTRO</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b7e4b843-4591-44b6-9748-4fc604e92a9d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ced9211e-4097-42e4-8872-5464fa812df2\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>회사정보</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7d489f47-c2fa-40ce-a360-3306122e7252\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> (간단한 정보 등)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-35dd7d4e-54e2-4b34-b3b9-32a2b25194c9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-03158e62-d64e-4037-8afe-9ac2ed779380\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>제품 소개</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a9c32087-4790-46d2-bac8-9bb2e54ab5c1\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> (제품 사진이나 텍스트, 사양 위주의 디자인 구성)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1fee4c31-54fe-4ca8-9839-28a4edf3a43f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2179ad63-75ce-4ffd-a5e3-42b55fb649b4\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>기타</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-90b2492d-9c21-4649-89ea-4420f9c00cb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223806623533/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c1d9e84e-ed46-42a9-8aa3-fc024810233c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d41e124d-9aa7-4439-8ddf-3fa62efbcdd6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-92a03ea8-48f4-4469-b935-07e1e85f1b43\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8ce500eb-0f7a-49e0-a205-ec718c821450\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>CI/BI 매뉴얼 가이드</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e00a00d0-0e2e-4c98-8f85-be2a29092aef\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f3837ba9-bee3-4f23-8526-5d53d58b9927\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄 홍보물의 꽃은 아무래도 CI GUIDE BOOK입니다. 이는 회사의 창업과 연관되어 있습니다. 창업 시 로고에서부터 슬로건 홍보물들의 타입 등등을 정의하여 진행하게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bd51935e-ea59-43ae-ba77-ed2bb0332e1f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ac59472a-0eed-49ca-8c99-fe9b5b4195f8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4f06fa1d-df39-44d9-951d-b987d15e472a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-42f552d9-b1c5-4d1c-978d-2737aed380c7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다만 이 CI 가이드북은 정말로 천차만별인 가격과 퀄리티로 인해 거의 많은 회사가 진행 여부를 두고 고민 중인 것으로 알고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a43d5fbc-3b31-451d-aca8-22cd441c2a04\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-559989b6-bf98-4b7f-8cd7-adb5ab874684\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-51c5b0fa-8c1e-43d1-b0a9-41d338fedf1e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-53518b84-4096-4ad2-b257-6ce9327b53b8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 초기에 한번 만들어 놓으면 두고두고 리뉴얼 때까지 활용할 수 있는 값어치 있는 것이 가이드북입니다. 반드시 제작할 것을 추천드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e6f1265d-5b98-4eb8-879c-31e16faba303\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d2a09b73-83d6-4973-a365-07c8d440788c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-46f00116-1744-49e2-a75e-0030b26b2a7d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a2d71194-4d56-44b2-8283-0cb5023ca2a4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또한 현재 국가에서 진행하는 브랜드나 로고 등도 여러 루트를 통해 지원금으로 제작할 수 있기 때문에 이 부분을 반드시 알아보시고 꼭 진행하기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0c59d7a7-eb8a-4b09-a784-b8c98664e06a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-55fb9607-bb37-4a12-9520-d8c373a8af42\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-466276e8-9c92-4755-a826-34dc94c4b43a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b3c8fc23-29e7-4afe-a17e-9c8dbbd8eba5\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>INTRO</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5d534ea8-15a1-4432-b786-fc31ee173d7a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ccdeea02-728e-4d53-8df3-7a6a92845328\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>CI/BI</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-32217f96-08a5-46d6-a37c-eabceb19a9ab\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> (가이드 내용)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a3c3d6cc-ebce-443e-ae71-e5ead40c25f9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d68f372e-a08e-41df-b0cc-fd6df68ad129\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>구성품 매뉴얼</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6c08ee23-e31b-4d59-a6ec-fa41224de87b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> (명함, 봉투, 배너, 유니폼, 차량 등의 구성 형태 가이드)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b06058d1-47c6-4166-8bc6-c17d6738f85b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e0b6ba23-1a59-4e24-aa55-e7774528f25b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>기타</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-588ac1d0-b595-4e37-8331-96cf743bce77\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-mod